      <title>Hindenburg 目标 Tingo 未能回应 SEC 欺诈诉讼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/hindenburg-target-tingo-fails-to-respond-to-sec-fraud-lawsuit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Tingo Group Inc. 是一家成为做空者报告对象的金融科技公司，由于未能回应美国证券交易委员会指控其夸大财务结果的诉讼，联邦法官裁定该公司及其首席执行官犯有欺诈罪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/hindenburg-target-tingo-fails-to-respond-to-sec-fraud-lawsuit</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 17:42:46 GMT</pubDate>
