      <title>交易员等待利率路径线索，美元走强导致黄金下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/gold-trades-near-record-as-fed-minutes-support-rate-cut-optimism</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美元走强，金价从上周的历史高点附近回落，导致这种贵金属对于大多数买家来说变得更加昂贵。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/gold-trades-near-record-as-fed-minutes-support-rate-cut-optimism</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 00:09:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
